rel="nofollow">Jeanine and Preston</a>.', 'Is Greek Yogurt a Father''s Day Superfood?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'is-greek-yogurt-a-fathers-day-superfood', '', '', '2011-05-31 09:12:24', '2011-05-31 16:12:24', '', 0, 'http://www.voskos.com/fresh/?p=960', 0, 'post', '', 0);

