(128, 583, 'Wendy', 'wdjulien@cogeco.ca', '', '173.238.106.152', '2010-12-29 14:11:55', '2010-12-29 21:11:55', 'I''ve been following Jenny since she began her "Recipes for Gals in Figure and Bodybuilding" Facebook page...for everyone btw, not just competitors (of which I am not)...which is also how I came across this site.  Jenny knows what she wants to say and afterall, it is her blog.  Her openness and sincerity in sharing her journey is what the focus should be here...the MESSAGE!  I don''t know Jenny personally, and yet she has inspired me (and countless others) to either begin, or stay on track of healthy living.\nThe tips she provides and products she endorses are beneficial to everyone involved.  Great job Jenny, yet again!', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(129, 583, 'Leslie', 'duckie1970@gmail.com', '', '68.228.174.201', '2011-01-04 20:52:53', '2011-01-05 03:52:53', 'I have just started really paying attention to Jenny on facebook.  Jenny your amazing.  There is so much on your pages and I want to start eating clean. Where do I start?  Is there anyway to ask for this yogurt to be delivered to Oklahoma?  Most of the products you use we do not get.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
