(146, 700, 'Hannah', 'osborne.baume@bigfoot.com', '', '178.199.65.93', '2011-01-09 17:20:07', '2011-01-10 00:20:07', 'Hi Jen! I have been checking out your FB page and blog for about a year, now, saving (and especially savouring!) many of the recipes you post. I REALLY appreciate you sharing this info as to how to prep foods, as I have been struggling with "too much of that, not enough of something else and Oh, my WORD, that just has to go in the bin NOW!" I prep lots of turkey meatballs and freeze them in advance for a quick snack or meal, but chopping, slicing dicing and cooking up so much in advance is really, really a great idea!\nThanks for all you do, and remember, you are loved and appreciated the world over! :-) &lt;&gt;', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
