(203, 1244, 'louisa', 'louami35@gmail.com', '', '76.94.35.60', '2013-07-16 21:31:48', '2013-07-17 04:31:48', 'I have seen your new packaging at Albertsons which was 5.3 oz instead of the 8 oz which I have been buying at Food For Less. There also was not a snap on top so that the container could be reused. \nI am very disappointed in your company for these changes. \nI have read that your new packaging is supposably to make additions to the yogurt easier. I often add fruit, etc to the existing containers and have not had any real difficulties with this.\nThis supposed convience certainly does not justify the decrease in amount which I assume will be sold at the same price nor the loss of being able to reuse the container.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
