(460, 1350, 'Linda Minutolo', 'lindaminutolo@hotmail.com', '', '67.236.11.70', '2012-04-22 14:33:22', '2012-04-22 21:33:22', 'I help to keep the earth clean by recyling as many items i can such as paper, plastics, cans, bottles.  I donate unused clothes and donate magazines to the library, dim or turn off lights, keep tv off if not watching, take reusable bags to supermarket, wash super loads of clothes or turn dial to small or medium loads to save water, use energy saving light bulbs, keep thermostat on highest or lowest comfortable setting according to season,turn computer off over night, do not waste food and i''m sure there are other things i do to help keep the earth clean.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
